Looking to leave a two-fight winless streak behind him, Manny Gamburyan will return to the octagon
on Sept. 27 in Las Vegas at 178 in a new weight class. Gamburyan is set to make his 135-pound men's
bantamweight debut against Cody "The Renegade" Gibson at the MGM Grand Arena on a pay-per-view card
headlined by the light heavyweight title fight between champion Jon Jones and Daniel Cormierr
